        >
            <source src='./video/mobileprototype.mp4' type='video/mp4'>
        </video>
    </div>
    <figcaption>Mobile prototype</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>
    With more feedback I prepared the desktop prototype which was tested internally to iron out
    remaining questions about scope of first iteration that we wanted to deliver.
</p>
<figure class='full'>
    <img
        srcset='
            images/desktopprototype-400.webp 400w,
