        width='905'
        height='564'
        loading='lazy'
    >
    <figcaption>Desktop prototype</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>
    Team delivered the feature on desktop first. It was rolled out as an A/B test and after initial
    observation we registered uptick in the key metrics that we hoped would benefit from feature's
    presence in users' experience.
</p>
<p>
    Because of this optimistic results the feature was rolled to mobile platforms too, and later was
    iterated on by my colleagues. Improved experience provided more data and included positive
    reinforcement messaging to drive those initial improvements for our metrics even higher.
</p>
